targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  bairro,
  funcionamento,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM semaforos
GROUP BY bairro, funcionamento
ORDER BY bairro, funcionamento;

SELECT
  latitude  AS lat,
  longitude AS lon,
  semaforo,
  bairro,
  tipo,
  funcionamento
FROM semaforos
WHERE latitude IS NOT NULL AND longitude IS NOT NULL;

SELECT
  latitude  AS lat,
  longitude AS lon,
  nome,
  endereco
FROM monitoramento_cttu
WHERE latitude IS NOT NULL AND longitude IS NOT NULL;

SELECT
  stop_lat AS lat,
  stop_lon AS lon,
  stop_id,
  stop_name
FROM gtfs_stops
WHERE location_type = 0
  AND stop_lat IS NOT NULL AND stop_lon IS NOT NULL;

SELECT
  latitude  AS lat,
  longitude AS lon,
  1 AS weight
FROM semaforos
WHERE latitude IS NOT NULL AND longitude IS NOT NULL;

SELECT
  id,
  name,
  tipo,
  ST_AsGeoJSON(geom)::json AS geojson
FROM faixaazul;

SELECT
  _id,
  equipamento,
  tipo,
  logradouro,
  velocidade_via,
  latitude  AS lat,
  longitude AS lon
FROM equipamentos_medicao_velocidade;

WITH base AS (
  SELECT
    'Janeiro' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_janeiro

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Fevereiro' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_fevereiro

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Marco' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_marco

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Abril' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_abril

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Maio' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_maio

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Junho' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_junho

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Julho' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_julho

  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    'Agosto' AS mes,
    hora,
    (qtd_31a40km + qtd_41a50km + qtd_51a60km + qtd_61a70km) AS veiculos
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_agosto
)

SELECT
  hora,
  SUM(veiculos) AS veiculos
FROM base
WHERE
  mes = '${mes}'
  AND (
    '${horario}' = 'Todo o dia'
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Pico manhã (07–09)'  AND hora BETWEEN 7  AND 9)
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Pico almoço (11–13)' AND hora BETWEEN 11 AND 13)
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Pico tarde (17–19)'  AND hora BETWEEN 17 AND 19)
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Noite (20–23)'       AND hora BETWEEN 20 AND 23)
  )
GROUP BY hora
ORDER BY hora;

WITH base AS (
  SELECT
    'Janeiro' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_janeiro

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    'Fevereiro' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_fevereiro

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    'Marco' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_marco

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    'Abril' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_abril

  -- Maio propositalmente ignorado

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    'Junho' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_junho

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    'Julho' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_julho

  UNION ALL

  SELECT
    'Agosto' AS mes,
    hora,
    qtd_0a10km       AS v_0a10,
    qtd_11a20km      AS v_11a20,
    qtd_21a30km      AS v_21a30,
    qtd_31a40km      AS v_31a40,
    qtd_41a50km      AS v_41a50,
    qtd_51a60km      AS v_51a60,
    qtd_61a70km      AS v_61a70,
    qtd_71a80km      AS v_71a80,
    qtd_81a90km      AS v_81a90,
    qtd_91a100km     AS v_91a100,
    qtd_acimade100km AS v_acima100
  FROM relatorio_fluxo_agosto
)

SELECT
  hora,
  SUM(v_0a10)     AS v_0a10,
  SUM(v_11a20)    AS v_11a20,
  SUM(v_21a30)    AS v_21a30,
  SUM(v_31a40)    AS v_31a40,
  SUM(v_41a50)    AS v_41a50,
  SUM(v_51a60)    AS v_51a60,
  SUM(v_61a70)    AS v_61a70,
  SUM(v_71a80)    AS v_71a80,
  SUM(v_81a90)    AS v_81a90,
  SUM(v_91a100)   AS v_91a100,
  SUM(v_acima100) AS v_acima100
FROM base
WHERE
  mes = '${mes}'
  AND (
    '${horario}' = 'Todo o dia'
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Pico manhã (07–09)'  AND hora BETWEEN 7  AND 9)
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Pico almoço (11–13)' AND hora BETWEEN 11 AND 13)
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Pico tarde (17–19)'  AND hora BETWEEN 17 AND 19)
    OR ('${horario}' = 'Noite (20–23)'       AND hora BETWEEN 20 AND 23)
  )
GROUP BY hora
ORDER BY hora;

SELECT
  TRIM(SPLIT_PART(endereco, '-', 1)) AS corredor_principal,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM monitoramento_cttu
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY total DESC;

SELECT
  TRIM(SPLIT_PART(logradouro, '-', 1)) AS corredor_principal,
  COUNT(*) AS total
FROM equipamentos_medicao_velocidade
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY total DESC
LIMIT 15;
